
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %> | CONSTIFIED SIGNATURE</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  
  <main>
    <section class="page-header">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <div class="breadcrumb">
          <a href="/">Home</a> / <span>About Us</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="about-intro">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="about-content">
          <div class="about-text">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>CONSTIFIED SIGNATURE was born from a passion for combining authentic Nigerian craftsmanship with contemporary design. Founded in 2018 in Imo State, our journey began with a simple mission: to showcase the exceptional talents of local artisans while creating footwear that stands shoulder-to-shoulder with global luxury brands.</p>
            <p>What started as a small workshop in Orlu has grown into a nationally recognized brand that celebrates the rich heritage of Nigerian leatherwork. Every pair of CONSTIFIED SIGNATURE shoes tells a story of tradition, innovation, and meticulous attention to detail.</p>
            <p>We believe that luxury should be ethical and sustainable. That's why we work directly with local craftsmen, ensuring fair wages and preserving traditional techniques that have been passed down through generations.</p>
            <div class="founder-quote">
              <blockquote>"Our vision is to elevate Nigerian craftsmanship to the global stage while creating footwear that combines comfort, durability, and timeless style."</blockquote>
              <cite>â€” Founder, CONSTIFIED SIGNATURE</cite>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-image">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/500/600" alt="Our Workshop">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="mission-values">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 class="section-title">Our Mission & Values</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="values-grid">
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-gem"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Quality Craftsmanship</h3>
            <p>We are committed to exceptional craftsmanship in every stitch, ensuring each pair of shoes meets our rigorous standards of quality and durability.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Ethical Production</h3>
            <p>We believe in fair trade practices, providing good working conditions and fair wages to all our artisans and partners.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Sustainability</h3>
            <p>We strive to minimize our environmental footprint by using responsibly sourced materials and implementing eco-friendly practices throughout our production process.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-globe-africa"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Cultural Heritage</h3>
            <p>We honor Nigeria's rich cultural heritage by incorporating traditional designs and techniques while evolving to meet contemporary fashion needs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="craftsmanship">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="craft-content">
          <div class="craft-image">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/500/600" alt="Craftsmanship">
          </div>
          <div class="craft-text">
            <h2>The Art of Craftsmanship</h2>
            <p>Every CONSTIFIED SIGNATURE product begins with carefully selected materials. We source the finest Nigerian leather, known for its remarkable durability and unique texture. Our materials are inspected by hand to ensure they meet our quality standards before entering our workshop.</p>
            <p>Our master craftsmen employ both traditional techniques and modern innovations to create footwear that stands the test of time. From hand-cutting the leather to meticulous stitching and finishing, each step in our process is executed with precision and care.</p>
            <p>It takes up to 72 hours to complete a single pair of CONSTIFIED SIGNATURE shoes, with over 200 individual steps from start to finish. This dedication to craftsmanship results in footwear that not only looks exceptional but provides lasting comfort and durability.</p>
            <a href="/collection/signature" class="btn secondary-btn">Explore Our Craftsmanship</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="team-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 class="section-title">Meet Our Team</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle">The dedicated professionals behind our brand</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-grid">
          <div class="team-member">
            <div class="member-image">
              <img src="/api/placeholder/300/300" alt="Team Member">
            </div>
            <div class="member-info">
              <h3>Chief Craftsman</h3>
              <p>With over 25 years of experience in leatherworking, our chief craftsman oversees quality and trains the next generation of artisans.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="team-member">
            <div class="member-image">
              <img src="/api/placeholder/300/300" alt="Team Member">
            </div>
            <div class="member-info">
              <h3>Head Designer</h3>
              <p>Combining traditional aesthetics with modern trends, our head designer creates timeless footwear that honors our cultural heritage.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="team-member">
            <div class="member-image">
              <img src="/api/placeholder/300/300" alt="Team Member">
            </div>
            <div class="member-info">
              <h3>Production Manager</h3>
              <p>Ensuring that each pair meets our exacting standards, our production manager coordinates the entire manufacturing process.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="team-member">
            <div class="member-image">
              <img src="/api/placeholder/300/300" alt="Team Member">
            </div>
            <div class="member-info">
              <h3>Customer Experience</h3>
              <p>Dedicated to your satisfaction, our customer experience team provides personalized service from purchase to delivery.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="testimonials-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 class="section-title">What Our Customers Say</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonials-slider">
          <div class="testimonial">
            <div class="testimonial-content">
              <p>"CONSTIFIED SIGNATURE shoes are the perfect blend of comfort and style. I've worn mine to multiple events and always receive compliments. The quality is exceptional, and I love supporting Nigerian craftsmanship."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <div class="author-image">
                <img src="/api/placeholder/80/80" alt="Testimonial Author">
              </div>
              <div class="author-info">
                <h4>Chioma A.</h4>
                <span>Lagos, Nigeria</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial">
            <div class="testimonial-content">
              <p>"As someone who values both quality and cultural heritage, I couldn't be happier with my purchase. The attention to detail is remarkable, and the shoes have held up beautifully despite daily wear."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <div class="author-image">
                <img src="/api/placeholder/80/80" alt="Testimonial Author">
              </div>
              <div class="author-info">
                <h4>Emmanuel O.</h4>
                <span>Abuja, Nigeria</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial">
            <div class="testimonial-content">
              <p>"Their Ankara print collection perfectly combines traditional patterns with modern design. I've ordered multiple pairs and the consistency in quality is impressive. Truly a standout Nigerian brand."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <div class="author-image">
                <img src="/api/placeholder/80/80" alt="Testimonial Author">
              </div>
              <div class="author-info">
                <h4>Grace E.</h4>
                <span>Port Harcourt, Nigeria</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="partners-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 class="section-title">Our Partners</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="partners-grid">
          <div class="partner">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/200/100" alt="Partner Logo">
          </div>
          <div class="partner">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/200/100" alt="Partner Logo">
          </div>
          <div class="partner">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/200/100" alt="Partner Logo">
          </div>
          <div class="partner">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/200/100" alt="Partner Logo">
          </div>
          <div class="partner">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/200/100" alt="Partner Logo">
          </div>
          <div class="partner">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/200/100" alt="Partner Logo">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <h2>Experience the CONSTIFIED SIGNATURE Difference</h2>
          <p>Step into comfort, style, and tradition with our handcrafted footwear collection.</p>
          <a href="/shop" class="btn primary-btn">Shop Our Collection</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>